*   [List of mathematical topics in relativity](/List_of_mathematical_topics_in_relativity): The differential geometry and tensor calculus required to describe spacetime curvature and gravitational phenomena.
*   [List of string theory topics](/List_of_string_theory_topics): The highly theoretical and mathematically intensive concepts underpinning the idea that fundamental particles are tiny vibrating strings.
